{"id":162968,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011621/","date":"2011-06-22T03:00:32Z","modified":"2011-06-22T03:40:43Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/6/21","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/06/20/asia-society-plans-exhibition-of-ai-weiwei-new-york-photos/?scp=2&#038;sq=ai%20weiwei&#038;st=cse\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国亚洲学会计划展出艾未未纽约摄影作品</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“这将给这位自四月以来被噤声的艺术家一个发出声音的机会”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋》月刊</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2011/06/is-the-china-model-failing/240773/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国模式面临失败？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国模式是建立在政府威胁对人民使用过度武力之基础上的，正如政府处理最近的骚乱所显示的那样</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/06/21/chinas-critical-disconnect/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的严重断裂</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中央对地方政府资助不够，使得北京和地方之间出现断裂，政策难于贯彻执行</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2011/jun/21/zebra-chinese-music-festival-scene\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在中国音乐节的幕后</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——四川斑马音乐节按西方标准看太温和了，但能举办这样的活动就是迈向艺术自由的重要一步</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-20/rising-wealth-is-the-way-to-fulfill-china-s-revolution-view.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">不断增加的财富实现中国的革命</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——研究表明，在没有政治自由、财产保障和司法公正的国家，生活水平的提高会遇到上限。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《澳大利亚人报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/sex-buddhism-and-ballroom-dancing-wikileaks-reveals-beijing-underbelly/story-e6frg6so-1226078073938\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">性、佛教和交谊舞——“维基解密”透露北京内幕</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">赫芬顿邮报</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/06/20/jon-huntsman-predicts-major-problems-for-china_n_880402.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">洪博培预言中国将面临“很大麻烦”</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“生活水平的提高使人民更意识到政治压迫，并对政府控制进行抵制”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约客》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/evanosnos/2011/06/the-party-politics-of-the-turtle-king.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国来信：小龟王与共产党</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——深圳关于电动自行车的禁令凸显当局削足适履的统治手段难以满足民众要求</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国听说</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinahearsay.com/critical-acclaim-for-jike-the-peoples-search-engine/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">嬉笑怒骂评“即刻”（人民的搜索引擎）</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“即刻”刚刚露面，对于它究竟应该如何发音和如何理解已经有了多种理论</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/06/21/china%E2%80%99s-doctrine-of-indifference/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的“无所谓”主义</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国接待利比亚正反双方，说明它已放弃了所谓“和平共处五项原则”的立场。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《印度时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics/nation/first-china-aircraft-carrier-sea-trial-next-week/articleshow/8936425.cms\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的航母下周下水试航</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——选择下周试航既是向南海地区展示实力，也是为了庆祝党的生日</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交事务委员会</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cfr.org/cybersecurity/role-cybersecurity-us-china-relations/p25318?cid=rss-asia-the_role_of_cybersecurity_in_u-062111&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+region%2Fasia+%28CFR.org+-+Regions+-+Asia%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">网络安全在中美关系中的地位</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中美双方对于网络空间的观点有着根本区别，因此未来在这个领域还会麻烦不断</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>IPS – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://ipsnews.net/news.asp?idnews=56154\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">针对伊朗互联网问题的新武器</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“手提箱里的互联网”可能会使伊朗的“国内互联网”计划失灵</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>Sinocism – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.sinocism.com/?p=1986\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">埃及的动乱会令中国政府更强大？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中共的注意力集中在三件事上：继续掌权、中国复兴和发家致富，他们会利用埃及的混乱为自己进行宣传</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约客》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/evanosnos/2011/06/in-china-huntsman-leaves-them-guessing.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国来信：洪博培让中国人摸不着头脑</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国对他宣布竞选总统反应冷淡，与他当年到北京赴任时受到的热情对待截然不同</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《新闻周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newsweek.com/2011/06/19/north-korea-s-meth-export.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北朝鲜的冰毒出口</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——朝鲜的地下毒品给中国的边境城市延吉带来大量问题</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110621/ap_on_re_as/as_vietnam_china_patrol\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中越进行联合海上巡逻</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“南海争端在中越之间造成了一些不和谐，但联合巡逻是个好兆头”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交事务</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/67926/andrew-j-nathan/what-china-wants\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国想要什么</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——评基辛格新书《论中国》</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">商业内幕</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/chinese-ghost-cities-overblown-2011-6?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+clusterstock+(ClusterStock)&#038;utm_content=Google+Reader\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">关于中国那</span>6500<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万空房</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——新的调查显示中国“只有”</span><span>1660</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万空房</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.forbes.com/greatspeculations/2011/06/20/is-chinese-manufacturing-coming-back-to-the-u-s/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国的制造业是否正从中国回流？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的优势正在被高通胀、高能源价格和日趋不稳的环境所消磨掉</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702304070104576397513517003444.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人民币升值一年却没得到表扬</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——去年人民币升值</span><span>5.5%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，加上通胀因素实际更高。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110621/bs_nm/us_chinese_banks\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的银行面临减速和紧缩</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国主要的银行股票价格近期跌到新低</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110621/bs_nm/us_china_accounting_tradehalts\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">独家：解决中国股票长期停牌的方案</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国证券业人士正在研究解决办法，防止中国上市股票因账目问题长期停牌的现象重演</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2011/jun/20/ryanair-designs-chinese-rival-boeing-737\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">瑞安航空击败波音与中国达成飞机设计协议</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——瑞安将于中国商用飞机公司共同设计</span><span>C919</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">飞机</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-06-20/huawei-global-consumer-push-leads-to-banned-facebook-youtube.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">华为利用被禁网站推广其消费产品</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——华为在</span><span>Facebook</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span>YouTube</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">等网站上推广自己的产品，在国际化战略上走到了其他中国公司的前面</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲哨兵</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.asiasentinel.com/index.php?option=com_content&#038;task=view&#038;id=3263&#038;Itemid=422\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的稀土开采灾难</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span><span>Google</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“中国稀土环境破坏”可以找到数百条报道，这些教训应该被准备开采稀土矿的国家所记取</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/global/2011/jun/21/comment\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的女权主义裹足不前</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——那些敢于与丑闻和虐待做斗争的女性面临着巨大的压力</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/omega-watch-gift-to-mao-in-chinese-propaganda-film-isnt-product-placement-director-says/2011/06/20/AGektucH_story.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国宣传影片《建党伟业》中的欧米伽金表不是软广告</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——毛泽东确实从女朋友那里得到过一款欧米伽表</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110621/ap_on_re_as/as_china_floods\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国</span>660<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">座水库面临决口危险</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——大雨导致的洪水已造成</span><span>175</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人死亡，</span><span>86</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人失踪和</span><span>50</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美元直接经济损失</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><br /></span></p>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-870615136242795204?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":464,"categories":[1],"tags":[3764,9154,19255]}